{"tid":476930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭多名警員襲擊和毆打 李小龍受傷向政府索償","createTime":"2017-11-22T12:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T03:45:13.000Z","uid":37757,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"62082190943ce23683c5e21e7f6a744a27fb598f","tid":476930,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:56:52.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】2014年佔領行動，Now新聞台工程人員李小龍在旺角採訪期間被警員指控襲警被捕，其後證據不足獲釋。李小龍入稟高等法院，就過程中受到的傷害向特區政府索償。<br />\n<br />\n當日事發後，本台工程人員李小龍在警員扣押下到醫院驗傷。<br />\n<br />\n李小龍星期三入稟高等法院向特區政府索償。入稟狀指，原告人李小龍在2014年11月25日晚上大約9時08分，在旺角上海街509號至511號附近，遭到多名警員襲擊和毆打至身體受到實際傷害，以及非法禁錮。過程中多名警員將李小龍按在到地上，重複和持續地坐着他、捏他、踩他和膝撞他，又用拳打他及用腳踢他，歷時大約分半鐘，李小龍之後感到暈眩以及全身痛楚。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指，以上襲擊行為對李小龍造成的傷勢，包括他左眼角、兩邊手肘、左手手指和膝頭磨損，左手和左肋骨受傷，右耳後面位置瘀傷，另外亦有創傷後壓力症候群以及精神和心理障礙。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀指，香港特區政府作為以上警員的僱主，在法律上對事件有替代責任向特區政府索取賠償。<br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台發表聲明，指入稟是李小龍個人決定，作為僱主全力支持他取回公道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=244164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D244164&d=Lrz33MO9%2FF%2BgA77gwrfowdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a9386610\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D244164&h=446f0d8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=244164</a>"},{"pid":"2e0d610d04be397b5d2dc5485503f1fdadbbc0c3","tid":476930,"uid":62710,"like":2,"dislike":48,"score":-46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:08:27.000Z","msg":"李小龍？邊L度李小龍呀？睇過"},{"pid":"e62599ac60b373e5ed09dab70a6547ed1d8460b1","tid":476930,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>李小龍？邊L度李小龍呀？睇過</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac49b4bdc72006be987e36708ee2ca9610b223a7","tid":476930,"uid":147113,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:09:48.000Z","msg":"我仲以為真個個李小龍起好多年前比警犬打"},{"pid":"e9e34282accc4ce4c8ebd5b617a064e5716c575a","tid":476930,"uid":49669,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:18:03.000Z","msg":"李小龍都會受傷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a3437ad0997072f9fb37ac8fc20edf81b0eab7","tid":476930,"uid":47558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"阿sir 做野唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e66d22270f75e0f1135c636cbef22380b2557a","tid":476930,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b21578d67c6f8e2af82d078b27c4e1939f3a17","tid":476930,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:28:24.000Z","msg":"邊個龍哥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c0dda21951f51fc564f496ab7931be036dcff3","tid":476930,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9007ed3b885c1ff8e963a93b741583d07673c321","tid":476930,"uid":36421,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vdpieo1j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvdpieo1j&h=ed8c1e95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5933524766f0c8ca53e72c92a4e7cf134e102b13","tid":476930,"uid":1248,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:48:45.000Z","msg":"好囉你未死咁就好囉"},{"pid":"0e8ca8412945053d30b18ad646f0e6392391b092","tid":476930,"uid":67485,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T13:49:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff2a67e95dc2e4521825623